code: @Override public int compare(CharSequence sequencedNode, CharSequence otherSequencedNode) {     if (sequencedNode == null && otherSequencedNode == null) {         return 0.     }     if (sequencedNode != null && otherSequencedNode == null) {         return 1.     }     if (sequencedNode == null && otherSequencedNode != null) {         return -1.     }     return super.compare(getZooKeeperSequenceNumber(sequencedNode), getZooKeeperSequenceNumber(otherSequencedNode)). }

private CharSequence getZooKeeperSequenceNumber(CharSequence sequencedNodeName) {     int len = sequencedNodeName.length().     return sequencedNodeName.subSequence(len - ZOOKEEPER_SEQUENCE_LENGTH, len). }
